<head>卍續藏 校注</head>
<p>
<note n="0414001" resp="#resp2" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0414001">羽一作鳥</note>
<note n="0414002" resp="#resp2" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0414002">鎖一作索</note>
<note n="0414003" resp="#resp2" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0414003">王一作主</note>
<note n="0414004" resp="#resp2" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0414004">人下一有每月滲經水且六字產下時神下頂字</note>
<note n="0414005" resp="#resp2" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0414005">若作並</note>
<note n="0414006" resp="#resp2" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0414006">將去二字在若穢之間</note>
<note n="0414007" resp="#resp2" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0414007">溪河洗澤作洗溪河</note>
<note n="0414008" resp="#resp2" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0414008">女下有不覺二字</note>
<note n="0414009" resp="#resp2" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0414009">候作俟</note>
<note n="0414010A" resp="#resp2" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0414010A">一無答字重字</note>
<note n="0414010B" resp="#resp2" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0414010B">一無答字重字</note>
<note n="0414011" resp="#resp2" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0414011">誦一作讀</note>
<note n="0414012" resp="#resp2" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0414012">散作悔</note>
<note n="0414013" resp="#resp2" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0414013">奈等六字作那落迦并變</note>
<note n="0414014" resp="#resp2" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0414014">中作地獄</note>
<note n="0414015" resp="#resp2" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0414015">便一作使</note>
<note n="0414016" resp="#resp2" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0414016">人上一有女字</note>
<note n="0414017" resp="#resp2" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0414017">復一作亦覆</note>
<note n="0414018" resp="#resp2" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0414018">說作諸</note>
<note n="0414019" resp="#resp2" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0414019">人下有說字</note>
<note n="0414020" resp="#resp2" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0414020">無得字</note>
</p>
